s required to have.  So long as you have a few warriors, you're ok.  So long as you have a shaman, you're okay.  But you need a bunch of clerics, every day, all the time.  That's pressure.  No other class is so heavily relied upon on such a daily basis at the high end game.  Every class has its role.  But unfortunately the role of the cleric is the most depended-upon roll in the high end game.<br>
<br>
Finnien, 60 Cleric<br>
Crusaders of Plilo<br>
<br>
